social_posts.post_text: This is your sneak peek at 2 items from our Showroom Exclusive sale! We’ve released these items over @sejspecials to get us warmed up for next week! Join me next Wednesday for the big reveal and then Friday dec. 9th at 8pm CST for our LIVE comment to claim sale.

Have you had a chance to try on the newest colors in the Lael collection? We are over the moon for these tiny darlings. Our lives may feel hectic from moment to moment, but like these gems, the ‘world’ cannot touch you. Lael is Hebrew for “belonging to God”, and we hope these earrings remind you that you are beloved and deeply cherished. Who in your life needs this as a reminder?⁠⠀
⁠⠀
BEST SELLER alert! These Unity earrings are flying. Wahoo! We love it.
MORE from our newest collection! "Anah" means "master of patience & perseverance." May this piece help you to extend patience to yourself and to those around you.

Have you been over to @sejspecials to comment to claim from our Showroom Exclusives? I can't wait to see what you love! 
- Summer

$500 in jewelry GIVEAWAY!

Okay gals, I've never done this before and might be the only time that I do, but here goes! :)

The winner of this giveaway will receive a collection of handpicked items from our Last Chance jewelry category. With Christmas coming up, you might win enough items to gift all the special ladies in your life with some amazing items (we promise to send you doubles of the best items to gift).

All you have to do is tag at least 2 of your friends who would love some SEJ, make sure you are following us and sign-up our email list (link is also in bio)!

If you are really hoping you win, for a bonus entry, like this and last post! And if you really like us & want to support small businesses share the post on your IG cause sharing is caring right?

Giveaway closes on Dec 16th at midnight.
